{"tid":2310320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲疑針對中國通過新例批准推翻與外國政府協議","createTime":"2020-12-03T07:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T17:02:36.000Z","uid":63543,"like":107,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e366382e1f918630737c9a8493df598cd6b75883","tid":2310320,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"澳洲國會通過法案，賦予聯邦政府權力否決澳洲各州份、理事會或機構與外國政府之間的任何協議，例如維多利亞州在2018年越過聯邦政府加入中國「一帶一路」合作協議。<br />\n<br />\n今次新規有可能會激怒中國，澳洲總理莫里森表示，澳洲的所有政策及規定都應該以國家利益而定，強調法案並不針對任何國家。<br />\n<br />\n根據新規的條款，如果外長認為與外國達成的協議不利澳洲外交或與外交政策不符，外長可以否決任何協議。莫里森曾表示，維多利亞州與中國達成的協議削弱聯邦政府的外交政策能力，但拒絕評論會否推翻該協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1060800&amp;newstype=91&amp;newssource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3DNOW.1060800%26newstype%3D91%26newssource%3DHK6&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c72e92bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/news.aspx?newsid=NOW.1060800&amp;newstype=91&amp;newssource=HK6</a>"},{"pid":"7063b0e00f64be88bd52f5806d7ffb2742a880aa","tid":2310320,"uid":19062,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"中國墨爾本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2161ebb5ec01c1100b2999b50313df3bb0739ed0","tid":2310320,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30034a997771246b1760c9c9a3e197b5540f6510","tid":2310320,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"光速師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95567836e050a27b7b107ad7741222caee1e76ea","tid":2310320,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ho